info.title: Create a generated video
info.description: Use text to create an AI generated video

post.description: Use text to create an AI generated video

prompt.title: prompt
prompt.description: User submitted text for a generated video. Keep the prompt to a maximum of 32 tokens.

previewImageMarkdown.title: Preview Image Markdown
previewImageMarkdown.description: A markdown string that, when rendered, displays the preview image of the generated video. The markdown should be in the format `![This is the preview image. Click to create your video.](Image URL)` to properly display the image with instructions.

videoUrlWithCTA.title: Video URL with Call to Action
videoUrlWithCTA.description: The URL where the generated video can be accessed, accompanied by a call to action. Format this as a markdown link with the text 'Click here to create your video' leading to the video URL, e.g., `[Click here to create your video](Video URL)`.
